              "free_text": [
                " First Irradiation, 3600 sec. Measurements for",
                "the first irradiation were carried out in two",
                "different configurations: a full stack of foils and",
                "the gallium oxide powder individually. The stack",
                "measurement was initially made at 30 cm for 1 h. The",
                "stack was then measured at 30 cm for 12 h. A final",
